ists/Chappell-Roan">Chappell Roan</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Kneecap">Kneecap</a>等人并列。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doechii-says-paramore-made-a-huge-impression-on-me-and-my-style-3823745">Doechii 的帖子称 Paramore“给我留下了深刻的印象，我的风格”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
