之都最近在7月19日在都柏林的伊维亚花园宣布了他们的“迄今为止最大的头条展览”。</a>他们将加入英国朋克二人组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-play">软游戏</a>-FKA<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slaves">奴隶</a>- 伦敦三人组和<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/mary-in-the-junkyard-18-11-2024-3813511">前<em>NME</em> Cover Stars。</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mary-in-the-junkyard">玛丽在垃圾场</a>。</p><p>门票将于本周五（12月20日）当地时间上午9点开始销售，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-murder-capital-tickets%2Fartist%2F5255545" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>获得。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>首先出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-murder-capital-share-impassioned-new-single-love-of-country-for-palestine-aid-3823753">谋杀资本份额的谋杀资本份额赋予巴勒斯坦援助的新单曲“爱情之爱”</a> 。</p> ;
